	   <tr><td colspan=2>HP is god. 50 hp is nothing?<br>Say that to the necros with base hp over 2000 unbuffed. I myself have 600hp added from items with 50-75 hp added, and while its a nice item i just cant see a necro needing this item. We take way too many hits soloing and while liching at the same time, every little bit helps, ive fd'd with 2hp before, and you can be sure it was because i had my hp gear on.<br><br>Wiz, dru, cler, mage, enc. Those are the classes i can see using this item. Any other class with a mana conversion (necro shaman) doesnt really need this. Only classes that need a higher base full mana would be a nuker healer or mezzer.<br><br>(hell im never full mana anyways)<br><br>Smlog TwishBish<br>60 warlock<br>D.ro -&gt; stormhammer<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
